metadata.name: Untitled Artwork #1/11
metadata.description:
The Auction is a digital painting for NFT Factory Paris as part of the X-Hack exhibition.  
The Auction takes us on a journey of painted, glitched realism as the auctioneer auctions two digital paintings of "Right Click and Save As Guy"   

Hi-res Jpeg  
Dimensions: 17717px X 11811px  
Circa 2023
